## 1. RBAC Enforcement ✅

**Files Changed:**
- [RoleMiddleware.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php) — New file
- [index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/index.php) — 16 routes updated

```diff
- })->add($authMiddleware);
+ })->add(RoleMiddleware::adminOnly())->add($authMiddleware);
```

**Verification:**
```bash
# Student → 403
{"success":false,"error":"Forbidden","your_role":"student"}

# Admin → 200
{"success":true,"users":[...]}
```

