## 2. Attendance API ✅

**Endpoints Added:**
- `POST /attendance/mark` — Insert/update attendance records
- `GET /attendance` — Fetch class attendance by date

**DB Evidence:**
```
+----------------+------------+---------+---------+
| gibbonPersonID | date       | type    | context |
+----------------+------------+---------+---------+
| 0000000002     | 2026-02-08 | Present | Person  |
| 0000000003     | 2026-02-08 | Absent  | Person  |
+----------------+------------+---------+---------+
```

