## 3. Frontend Route Guards ✅

**Files Changed:**
- [ProtectedRoute.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/components/ProtectedRoute.tsx) — New file
- [AppRoutes.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/routes/AppRoutes.tsx) — 12 routes wrapped

**Usage:**
```tsx
<ProtectedRoute allowedRoles={['admin']}>
  <AdminDashboard />
</ProtectedRoute>
```

