## 4. Dashboard APIs ✅

**Endpoints Added:**
- `GET /student/dashboard` — Profile, attendance, notifications, classes
- `GET /teacher/dashboard` — Profile, classes taught, attendance stats
- `GET /employee/dashboard` — Profile, notifications, notices

**Response Example (Student):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "profile": {"id": "0000000003", "name": "s User"},
    "attendance_summary": [{"status": "Absent", "count": 1}],
    "notifications": [],
    "today_classes": []
  }
}
```

